title._content: Berit Wallenberg's family at Viken, Lovö, Uppland, Sweden

description._content: Berit Wallenberg's family at their home Viken on Lovö Island west of Stockholm city. Her younger brother Carol, her mother Beatrice, born Keiller, and her father Oscar. Berit Wallenbergs familj vid deras hem Viken på Lovön väster om Stockholm. Hennes yngre bror Carol, hennes mor Beatrice, född Keiller, och hennes far Oscar. Parish (socken): Lovö Province (landskap): Uppland Municipality (kommun): Ekerö County (län): Stockholm Photograph by: Berit Wallenberg Date: 09.08.1925 Format: Film Persistent URL: kmb.raa.se/cocoon/bild/show-image.html?id=16001000052660 Read more about the photo database (in english): www.kms.raa.se/cocoon/bild/about.html
